reviewText:
This is on You Tube for free, so why pay for it? What REALLY gets me is this in the ad at the end...

"This DVD comes in a paper sleeve (NO BOX) which reduces costs to the consumer and landfill waste. GO GREEN with the paper sleeve. "

SO....since you want me to pay for LESS to go green how about SAVING us some green since you save all the printing & shipping cost's? How about that?
